===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Diantha (Masters)}}
Diantha forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Diantha|Gardevoir}}, {{p|Keldeo}}, {{Shiny}} {{p|Diancie}}, and {{p|Tyrantrum}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Both her Gardevoir and Shiny Diancie are capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Diantha became a playable sync pair on March 31, 2021.

Diantha has been featured on the title screen since the game's release and first appeared as an NPC during the [[story event]] [[Shining Heart of Dragons]]. She has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. 

